{"tid":1367199,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"環時總編輯：極端反對派休想用香港這種亂法要脅中央","createTime":"2019-07-26T07:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T08:19:04.000Z","uid":283021,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"20cb0522aecbb2eb81338fcfd454acbdbb60c3f4","tid":1367199,"uid":283021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"內地《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進發表文章，談到香港近期發生的事，包括國徽被污損， 指出內地有強大的國家機器，包括駐港部隊，為何收拾不了那一小撮暴徒，他認為，這就是一國兩制。<br />\n<br />\n文章說，香港這種亂法亂不到內地，極端反對派休想用這種亂要脅中央。但香港如果從此就無政府主義下去，就會失去國際金融中心地位，所有核心競爭力與優勢成為泡影。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">北京不出手，香港會接著亂一陣，但如果北京出手，要受「破壞一國兩制」的指責</span>。胡錫進說，他作為內地的一個媒體人，主張寧願北京不出手。<br />\n<br />\n文章最後認為，應該做的是，一、繼續勸他們。二、心疼地看著香港社會變亂變窮。三、耐心等待他們跌大跤後覺醒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470607-20190726.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470607-20190726.htm&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljndxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=d6107fb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470607-20190726.htm&h=f56a5f56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470607-20190726.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n亂一陣？"},{"pid":"97b060a0eb7b21f072b4ed46811d33bdd5693ab6","tid":1367199,"uid":283021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:43:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5283d5aab6e5afb37edc1ed4577bd4455e8eca0b","tid":1367199,"uid":65218,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/26/154506_19143249fd33d048611102e86fc30974.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F26%2F154506_19143249fd33d048611102e86fc30974.gif&h=ce1130c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99edefcf01262524ec3f60cac207aa5140dd5e74","tid":1367199,"uid":106544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score